  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      128.89,
      514.53,
      169.77
    ],
    "text": "Investigations were initiated by the Peliyagoda Police Station following information received on the morning of 24.05.2026 that a person had been attacked with a sharp weapon on Dutugemunu Mawatha within the Peliyagoda Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      184.21,
      467.91,
      211.29
    ],
    "text": "The deceased has been identified as a 51-year-old resident of Viharagama, Divulankadawala.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      225.85,
      522.7,
      252.96
    ],
    "text": "Preliminary investigations have revealed that a dispute between the deceased and another group escalated, resulting in the fatal attack carried out using a sharp weapon.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      267.52,
      515.7,
      294.6
    ],
    "text": "The suspect involved in the incident has been arrested, and further investigations are being conducted by the Peliyagoda Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
